Unihoms products help you control home appliances. You can simply ask Alexa to control your smart home device.
After connecting Alexa to your Unihoms products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our Unihoms " app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register an account in our " Unihoms " app;
(3). You need to have some Unihoms devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our " Unihoms " app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in " Unihoms " skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search " Unihoms " skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of " Unihoms ", and you'll be navigated to " Unihoms " login page;
(9). Follow the instructions on the page to complete the linking;
(10). Now all setup is finished.
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the bedroom light.”
“Alexa, turn off the bedroom light.”
“Alexa, set the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa, brighten the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa, dim the bedroom light to 50%.”
"Alexa, set bedroom light to green."
"Alexa, set bedroom light to cool white."
